snippet.textDisplay: Brilliantly explained detailed video on how this vaccine works. One wouldn’t need a Bio-chemical Engineering degree to understand the basics of how this works. Thanks for the video because I now know what to expect as I have the first dose of AstraZeneca, very useful to know.
